# evidence/model_guidance_snapshots/
# Runtime output directory for Model Research Agent (Batch 0.1).
# One YAML file per model per production batch:
#   {timestamp}_{model_id}.yaml
# e.g.:
#   20260430T153000Z_midjourney.yaml
#   20260430T153000Z_chatgpt_image.yaml
#   20260430T153000Z_nano_banana.yaml
#   20260430T153000Z_kling_omni.yaml
#
# All files validate against schemas/model_guidance_snapshot.schema.json.
# Files are plain git (text YAML) — not LFS-tracked.
# Generated by: python scripts/agents/run_pipeline.py --mode refresh-model-guidance
